<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8" standalone="no"?><?Xpress productLine="ncc-clause" ?><clause id="_47e9be0d-b00f-4b78-a2c9-9a9de499d04c" outputclass="ncc-clause"><meta><facet building="Class 1a"/><facet building="Class 1b"/><facet building="Class 10a"/><facet building="Class 10b"/><facet building="Class 10c"/></meta><sptc>S6C4</sptc><title id="_284f7da9-9f0b-4baa-b085-9d74213db0d3">Walls of shafts and fire-isolated exits generally</title><archive-num>2019: Spec C1.8: 3.2</archive-num><subclause id="_2e277bb2-f54a-47c0-b5bd-3908cc6d06bb" outputclass="subclause"><title id="_2bec8634-9a9f-4528-9c21-71deadcf4abe">SubClause</title><num>1</num><p>A wall of <xref format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/5e2c1f63-e589-4ce1-95e8-5c3e286a7aff/1359_0.4.0.xml#_2cf43983-ddc7-4b7f-b16e-2d3ed619886e" id="_e082d16e-7b8d-4a38-95a9-2cea8ce52de6" scope="local" type="abcb-glossentry">lightweight construction</xref> that is required to be <xref format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/5e2c1f63-e589-4ce1-95e8-5c3e286a7aff/1292_2.2.0.xml#_2d22acf1-980a-4a51-a1a7-758f41e54a83" id="_05edcf66-93f4-4e02-97fe-4ba88ba03af6" referencetype="Text" scope="local" synctargettext="false" type="abcb-glossentry">fire-resisting</xref> and which bounds a lift <xref format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/5e2c1f63-e589-4ce1-95e8-5c3e286a7aff/1459_26.0.0.xml#_99391afe-5794-47e4-94ab-7e9e7a83740a" id="_f088df51-1377-4261-a48c-675ff57f9079" scope="local" type="abcb-glossentry">shaft</xref>, stair <xref format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/5e2c1f63-e589-4ce1-95e8-5c3e286a7aff/1459_26.0.0.xml#_99391afe-5794-47e4-94ab-7e9e7a83740a" id="_00d8e035-df92-4d99-aeca-020bf61c25eb" scope="local" type="abcb-glossentry">shaft</xref>, or service <xref format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/5e2c1f63-e589-4ce1-95e8-5c3e286a7aff/1459_26.0.0.xml#_99391afe-5794-47e4-94ab-7e9e7a83740a" id="_164a6517-4e48-4229-a8c0-616cd57b0383" scope="local" type="abcb-glossentry">shaft</xref>, <xref format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/5e2c1f63-e589-4ce1-95e8-5c3e286a7aff/1283_2.0.0.xml#_2f0af1de-a7c1-44b9-a8b5-1faaedfdb023" id="_25fb6f36-a600-40c9-a0b7-4224b22bf555" scope="local" type="abcb-glossentry">fire-isolated passageway</xref> or <xref format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/5e2c1f63-e589-4ce1-95e8-5c3e286a7aff/1284_2.0.0.xml#_cfa6cc89-aa6c-4eaf-90e6-8aabe04b9c76" id="_435c0dee-0bcb-41de-ba01-dad3676f8252" scope="local" type="abcb-glossentry">fire-isolated ramp</xref> must be subjected to the following tests and must fulfil the following criteria:</p><ol outputclass="alpha"><li id="_e17cdec4-8801-419f-8c14-169f91a8bad6">The materials tests of <xref format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/5e2c1f63-e589-4ce1-95e8-5c3e286a7aff/451_0.10.0.xml#_01970f4e-35e1-4b15-8dc3-19800e1733ae" id="_5e10ba61-5937-4b7d-a512-d9beb24e2997" scope="local" type="clause">S6C10(a)</xref> and the criteria of <xref format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/5e2c1f63-e589-4ce1-95e8-5c3e286a7aff/456_21.3.0.xml#_b22e83a0-9a8d-40ae-847e-629a6d96dc76" id="_5ee148d3-b8f8-4aa8-a888-ba268fa91340" scope="local" type="clause">S6C11(a)</xref>.</li><li id="_ff7360ae-1687-44c2-835a-8c93ec378fb0">A static test by the imposition of a uniformly distributed load of 0.35 kPa (or its equivalent) in accordance with <xref format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/5e2c1f63-e589-4ce1-95e8-5c3e286a7aff/451_0.10.0.xml#_01970f4e-35e1-4b15-8dc3-19800e1733ae" id="_2e8640f6-c5ba-4b15-a07c-e248761ba5d5" scope="local" type="clause">S6C10(b)</xref> and the damage and deflection criteria of <xref format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/5e2c1f63-e589-4ce1-95e8-5c3e286a7aff/456_21.3.0.xml#_b22e83a0-9a8d-40ae-847e-629a6d96dc76" id="_ce945413-6965-4f67-a671-6f26748ae15b" scope="local" type="clause">S6C11(b)</xref> and <xref format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/5e2c1f63-e589-4ce1-95e8-5c3e286a7aff/456_21.3.0.xml#_b22e83a0-9a8d-40ae-847e-629a6d96dc76" id="_9c0b1886-873c-458f-a71e-838d7617ed6c" scope="local" type="clause">(c)</xref> respectively.</li><li id="_b6e52ecb-1f89-4f4a-a3f8-81fa9e2f8bf9">A dynamic test by the fall of the impact bag through a height of 150 mm in accordance with <xref format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/5e2c1f63-e589-4ce1-95e8-5c3e286a7aff/451_0.10.0.xml#_01970f4e-35e1-4b15-8dc3-19800e1733ae" id="_7e4ce5d2-08a3-44a0-ac03-05506aab9f04" scope="local" type="clause">S6C10(c)</xref> and the damage and deflection criteria of <xref format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/5e2c1f63-e589-4ce1-95e8-5c3e286a7aff/456_21.3.0.xml#_b22e83a0-9a8d-40ae-847e-629a6d96dc76" id="_90329ab1-8bb6-42e0-9189-4942259e1d5a" scope="local" type="clause">S6C11(b)</xref> and <xref format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/5e2c1f63-e589-4ce1-95e8-5c3e286a7aff/456_21.3.0.xml#_b22e83a0-9a8d-40ae-847e-629a6d96dc76" id="_31dc7313-83a8-40a7-95cd-97b8877b0034" scope="local" type="clause">(d)</xref> respectively.</li><li id="_ab23ca8f-3085-492f-bb19-76856afd63ba">The surface indentation test of <xref format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/5e2c1f63-e589-4ce1-95e8-5c3e286a7aff/451_0.10.0.xml#_01970f4e-35e1-4b15-8dc3-19800e1733ae" id="_95bd96e2-2bdd-41bf-bc99-287539024160" scope="local" type="clause">S6C10(d)</xref> and the surface indentation criterion of <xref format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/5e2c1f63-e589-4ce1-95e8-5c3e286a7aff/456_21.3.0.xml#_b22e83a0-9a8d-40ae-847e-629a6d96dc76" id="_5ebfa0ac-dfcb-4a36-969a-381e441abad7" scope="local" type="clause">S6C11(e)</xref>.</li></ol></subclause></clause>